  <description type="morphology">Plants to 12 cm. Stem leaves slightly concave, (1.1–)1.4–1.9 mm wide; margins often broadly incurved at base of acumen; apex frequently falcate, acumen slender, slightly channeled; medial laminal cells 30–70 × 5–7 µm; cells of clasping auricles smaller, rectangular to rhomboidal. Branch leaves spreading, concave, 0.8–1.9 × 0.3–1.2 mm; base slightly or not cordate-clasping; apex acuminate to abruptly acute, straight. Seta 1.2–4 cm. Capsule ellipsoid, neck short, 1.6–2.7 mm.</description>
